@node introduction "Introduction"
@prev main
@next AuthorityLaw
 
 I had made MB for private use, but I decided to  release it and let
 everyone  use  it. I  had used many  different sources  to  make MB
 (books, magazines, internet etc.). Next version will be released as
 soon as I get 50 new  English and 50 new Polish lyrics. If you want
 to see  it soon,  send me  some texts.  All kinds of lyrics will be
 accepted  (even your own band) except  nazi, country and disco polo
 (Polish kind of disco :). @{"Here" link AboutAuthor} is my address.
@endnode

@node authoritylaw "Authority law"
@prev Introduction
@next requierements

 Please, do not understand  that work as a  breaking of a copyright law.
 I only want to  appreciate  my hard work (if you don't believe - try to
 do it yourself..:-). MB  is mailware,  so if you  use it often  please,
 send  me a mail, letter or postcard. Of course I'll ge glad to see some
 money but you don't have to do that - it's not a shareware.

 You are not allowed to make any changes in guide.  If you find anything
 to correct - let me know and I'll do that.

 All suggestions, infos, greetings send to address in chapter @{"about author" link AboutAuthor}.
@endnode

