@node instruction "Instruction"
 It's as easy as fitting Amiga in Micronic tower 8-).

 First, you  have  to  choose  language  (Polish or English), then band
 and song. That's all.

 All lyrics contain also:
 - name of the performer
 - title of the song
 - title of the album
 - names, surname or nick of a person, who sent that text.

 Misterious number you can find there, is a number of version of MB with
 that lyrics appearing for the first time. You can also find the list of
 all songs in text file  "Index".  In "data"  drawer you  can find files
 with texts of all bands. You can view it separately without running MB.
 Simply load it into any guide viewer.

 Option "Search"  in  menu  are  available  only  when the "SearchGuide"
              © Gérard Cornu is in the C: directory.
@endnode

